13:46:25</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n\n<p><img src=\"/example.jpg\"><br><a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/tianjuewudi/article/details/112504019?ops_request_misc=&amp;request_id=&amp;biz_id=102&amp;utm_term=hexo%20cover.json&amp;utm_medium=distribute.pc_search_result.none-task-blog-2~all~sobaiduweb~default-0-.first_rank_v2_pc_rank_v29&amp;spm=1018.2226.3001.4187\">https://blog.csdn.net/tianjuewudi/article/details/112504019?ops_request_misc=&amp;request_id=&amp;biz_id=102&amp;utm_term=hexo%20cover.json&amp;utm_medium=distribute.pc_search_result.none-task-blog-2~all~sobaiduweb~default-0-.first_rank_v2_pc_rank_v29&amp;spm=1018.2226.3001.4187</a><br>@<a href=\"%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%85%AC%E4%BC%97%E5%8F%B7%EF%BC%9A%E7%89%A9%E8%A7%A3%E5%91%B3%E5%8D%9C%E6%85%A2%E8%AF%86%E5%A0%82\">想吃桃</a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210116100847807.jpg?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3FxXzQ0Nzc3MjUx,size_1,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center\" alt=\"((这里写自定义目录标题))\"></p>\n","raw":null,"categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"CoDesign","slug":"CoDesign","date":"2022-03-09T11:33:24.000Z","updated":"2022-03-09T11:33:24.000Z","comments":true,"top":null,"path":"api/articles/CoDesign.json","realPath":null,"excerpt":null,"keywords":"医疗互动 02 00 25","cover":"http://imageproxy.chaoxing.com/0x0,q15,jpeg,sJaLyZwRFnF3NB2MMdrC0FpqNMdssKrv_kEfKf57TU1c/https://p.ananas.chaoxing.com/star3/origin/0a095458f4662893205afe5d4865ef18.png","content":"<link rel=\"stylesheet\" class=\"aplayer-secondary-style-marker\" href=\"/assets/css/APlayer.min.css\"><script src=\"/assets/js/APlayer.min.js\" class=\"aplayer-secondary-script-marker\"></script><p><img src=\"http://imageproxy.chaoxing.com/0x0,q15,jpeg,sJaLyZwRFnF3NB2MMdrC0FpqNMdssKrv_kEfKf57TU1c/https://p.ananas.chaoxing.com/star3/origin/0a095458f4662893205afe5d4865ef18.png\" alt=\"CoDesign\"></p>\n<p>CoDesign 是腾讯自研的一站式产品设计协作平台，支持在线导入和预览设计稿，可以帮助互联网产品设计团队提升协作效率，让产品设计更加高效。加入地址<a href=\"https://wechat.design/standard/download/brand\">https://wechat.design/standard/download/brand</a><br><a href=\"https://codesign.qq.com/workspace/project/dqN292ggRO0aBXe\">https://codesign.qq.com/workspace/project/dqN292ggRO0aBXe</a></p>\n","raw":null,"categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"日语","slug":"日语中，“Omakase”","date":"2024-06-20T01:25:00.000Z","updated":"2024-09-29T22:09:35.000Z","comments":true,"top":null,"path":"api/articles/日语中，“Omakase”.json","realPath":null,"excerpt":null,"keywords":"医疗互动 02 00 25","cover":null,"content":"<link rel=\"stylesheet\" class=\"aplayer-secondary-style-marker\" href=\"/assets/css/APlayer.min.css\"><script src=\"/assets/js/APlayer.min.js\" class=\"aplayer-secondary-script-marker\"></script><p>答：”Omakase” 的日语读音为 &#x2F;oʊməˈkɑːseɪ&#x2F;<br>问：不是&#x2F;omə’keɪs&#x2F;吗￼我记得元辅e是开音节来着<br>答：在日语中，“Omakase” 的标准发音与英语的发音规则不同。你的问题涉及到不同语言的发音区别。让我们区分一下：</p>\n<p>1.日语发音：<br>•日语中的 “おまかせ” (Omakase) 发音是逐个音节发出来的，音标为 &#x2F;o̞.ma.ka.se&#x2F;。其中的 “e” 发音更接近于英语中的短音 [ɛ]，类似于 “set” 中的 “e”。日语中的 “おお其中的 “e”发音更接近于英语中的短音 []，类似于 “set” 中的 “e”。<br>2.英语借词发音：<br>•如果在英语中，“Omakase” 有时会按英语发音规则进行近似发音。你提到的 &#x2F;omə’keɪs&#x2F; 属于英语化的发音，其中的 &#x2F;keɪ&#x2F; 部分反映了英语中 “e” 在开音节中的发音（类似 “say” 中的发音）。<br>•这个发音 (&#x2F;omə’keɪs&#x2F;) 不是标准日语发音，而是英语母语者对日语词汇的一种适应性发音。</p>\n<p>总结：在日语中，“Omakase” 的 “e” 并不发长音 &#x2F;eɪ&#x2F;，而是短音 &#x2F;e&#x2F;。如果是在英语语境中借用这个词，可能会被发成 &#x2F;omə’keɪs&#x2F;。</p>\n","raw":null,"categories":[{"name":"122","path":"api/categories/122.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Typora","path":"api/tags/Typora.json"},{"name":"Markdown","path":"api/tags/Markdown.json"}]},{"title":"淘宝咸鱼","slug":"淘宝咸鱼","date":"2021-07-09T10:01:04.000Z","updated":"2021-07-09T10:01:04.000Z","comments":true,"top":null,"path":"api/articles/淘宝咸鱼.json","realPath":null,"excerpt":null,"keywords":"医疗互动 02 00 25","cover":"../medias/20.png","content":"<link rel=\"stylesheet\" class=\"aplayer-secondary-style-marker\" href=\"/assets/css/APlayer.min.css\"><script src=\"/assets/js/APlayer.min.js\" class=\"aplayer-secondary-script-marker\"></scr